object.customQuery:
WITH max_batch_id AS (
  SELECT COALESCE(MAX(batch_id), 1) AS batch_id
  FROM "$$metal_schema".batch_load_summary
),
latest_batch AS (
  SELECT 
    bls.batch_id,
    bls.source_start_cutoff_datetime,
    bls.source_end_cutoff_datetime
  FROM "$$metal_schema".batch_load_summary bls
  WHERE bls.source_system_code = '$$sourcesystemcode'
  QUALIFY ROW_NUMBER() OVER (ORDER BY bls.batch_id DESC) = 1
)

SELECT 
  mb.batch_id AS batch_id,
  lb.source_start_cutoff_datetime,
  lb.source_end_cutoff_datetime
FROM max_batch_id mb
LEFT JOIN latest_batch lb ON TRUE;
